{"tid":1507030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求 可以？不可以？","createTime":"2019-08-26T04:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T04:03:02.000Z","uid":236538,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"062a70f73f440cd4228a7af63f1c84601f9cabfd","tid":1507030,"uid":236538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:01:12.000Z","msg":"而家訴求已經表達得好清晰<br />\n<br />\n而政府一直無回應<br />\n<br />\n仲妄想開平台<br />\n<br />\n但其實大家都知<br />\n<br />\n我地無餘地同方法同政府商量<br />\n<br />\n我覺得一直咁樣消耗落去好無意義<br />\n<br />\n佢係回應唔到我地<br />\n<br />\n咁倒不如問佢一聲<br />\n<br />\n可以？定不可以 滿足五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n可以既 歡迎再傾細節<br />\n<br />\n唔可以既 唯有戰場相見<br />\n<br />\n唔可以再比政府含糊推搪過去<br />\n<br />\n當然<br />\n<br />\n政府一定唔會正視+回覆可唔可以滿足到民間五大訴求呢條問題<br />\n<br />\n所以我強烈建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月30日前<br />\n<br />\n政府必須回答可以/不可以滿足五大訴求</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我相信好多人仲有一絲希望 <br />\n望香港政府會因為國際壓力跪低回應到我地五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n但一味無限等落去 無論對邊一方都無益處<br />\n<br />\n9月30號前五大訴求仲係無回應<br />\n<br />\n我地10月1號直接送份生日禮物比共產黨好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e889ac71d2c470272bbc04a225a463be87c0c2","tid":1507030,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:02:51.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY95k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=0e9edfac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n----------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英文文宣建議：</strong></span><br />\n內容:<br />\n91 Hong Kong International Airport<br />\nSOS: Humanitarian Crisis Alert<br />\nGovernment has failed us. Police shot us.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s now or never, please stand with HK.<br />\nThanks in advance for your support and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n方向/ 建議：<br />\n-強調事態之緊急及嚴重<br />\n-形式係事先通知，而非道歉，機場示威是出師有名同埋其中既正當性<br />\n-例如可用&rdquo;SOS&rdquo;之字眼<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kZESP.jpg&h=ba0a90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLLrqSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLLrqSL.jpg&h=724c5863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d134df84993ff3fd9f300e90a850f28a37d2f60","tid":1507030,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:03:02.000Z","msg":"攬炒, 完"}]}